	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've done it, it's very easy. Just change the battery first and then use the "Fix GAR" function to reload the RAM in the device. Buying a CopyNES just for this purpose is a bit extreme though. I'd do it no charge, just cover return shipping. Otherwise, I think nesreproductions offers this service as well, not sure what they charge offhand though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


