	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I've done this service for a few video game stores.  The GAR SRAM content is not supplied with the copyNES software.  You need to find an image elsewhere.
<br />
<br />As far as backing up what's there...  No point.  It always changes!  Every time you backup the unit, it's never the same.  And I've never had issues moving SRAM content from one unit to another.
<br />
<br />The biggest issue most people would find is actually installing the new battery.  Finding the correct battery holder that fits in there is a PAIN.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


